room_title: Escape room "Jail Break" by Escape Cocoa Beach in Melbourne
room_address: 5675 N Atlantic Ave Unit 113/114 Cocoa Beach, FL 32931
room_description: It’s the mid-1970’s and you have been wrongfully accused and arrested by a small-town Sheriff. He has you in a holding cell next to his office. You must find your way to freedom while retrieving the evidence he holds against you. He plans to take you in front of the judge and prosecutor after his lunch break. You have only one hour…
